================================
pickle-secure: encrypted pickles
================================

.. image:: https://github.com/spapanik/pickle-secure/actions/workflows/build.yml/badge.svg
  :alt: Build
  :target: https://github.com/spapanik/pickle-secure/actions/workflows/build.yml
